info.+content: デリシャスパーティ♡プリキュア

The Recipepi fairies appear whenever a good meal is made and protect its taste. When a gang of phantom thieves called the Bundoru Gang start stealing Recipepis from Oiishina Town, the magical kingdom of CooKingdom sends a search party captain, Rosemary, alongside three energy fairies to retrieve the Recipepis. Rosemary soon meets Yui Nagomi, a girl who loves food. Yui teams up with the energy fairy Kome-Kome to become the Pretty Cure, Cure Precious. Alongside her fellow Pretty Cures, Yui begins to rescue the kidnapped Recipepis.
"Cheers! Delicious Party♡Precure" (Cheers！デリシャスパーティ♡プリキュア) by Machico
#2: "Delicious Heart" (ココロデリシャス) by Rico Sasaki (eps 21-26, 31-45)
#3: "Welcome, Children To♡Dreamia" (ようこそ、お子さま♡ドリーミア) by Moeha Nochimoto (eps 27-30)
"Bonds♡Specialty" (キズナ♡スペシャリティ) by Hana Hishikawa, Risa Shimizu, Yuka Iguchi and Ai Kayano (ep 44)
